		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent"> but why that stage specifically? How would the signal look different if it was (0°, 120°) or (120°, 240°) instead?</div>It's not that specific stage --- as I wrote before, the absolute phase of the color subcarrier is actually undefined, so it might as well be 0°/120° or 120°/240°.

		

